headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust Announces Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date and Conference Call Information
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) will announce its third quarter 2025 earnings results before market open on Friday, October 31, 2025. The Company will host a conference call on Friday, October 31 at 9:00 AM ET.

headline: Is Federal Realty Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
summary: Although Federal Realty has lagged the S&P 500 Index over the past year, analysts remain reasonably upbeat about the stock’s future performance.
